  "detailed_description": "Tile Tale is a game where you push tiles into a grid. The amount of tiles you have is limited and once you've used up all your tiles, the game ends. <br>If you form geometric fields of the same tile type, for example, a 2 by 2 of forest tiles, you score points and gain new tiles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/dcff7ef196f72181cb296e370ff4280f.poster.avif?t=1655559416\" width=560 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/dcff7ef196f72181cb296e370ff4280f.webm?t=1655559416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/dcff7ef196f72181cb296e370ff4280f.mp4?t=1655559416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Complete challenges to unlock new content!<br>Find all the different tile types. A lot of them have their own special rules!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/191ed0645c275d989d4fb4657fa1a068.poster.avif?t=1655559416\" width=560 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/191ed0645c275d989d4fb4657fa1a068.webm?t=1655559416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/191ed0645c275d989d4fb4657fa1a068.mp4?t=1655559416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Create cool worlds, like islands, swamps or mountain ranges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/bcff6e29b95c56c9d3d431e581431a2a.poster.avif?t=1655559416\" width=560 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/bcff6e29b95c56c9d3d431e581431a2a.webm?t=1655559416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/bcff6e29b95c56c9d3d431e581431a2a.mp4?t=1655559416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Construct a special building tiles, like windmills, a town hall or a rocket! Each building has its own special ability. For example, the windmill turns surrounding grasslands into wheat field tiles each turn. Wheat field tiles yield a lot of points, but less new tiles when combined.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/2ad4bf729fb41b4cf118649f87e1f965.poster.avif?t=1655559416\" width=560 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/2ad4bf729fb41b4cf118649f87e1f965.webm?t=1655559416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/2ad4bf729fb41b4cf118649f87e1f965.mp4?t=1655559416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Beware of portals. They spawn evil creatures that corrupt your tiles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/c9605dd8b61f5542e6c3782e269e69dc.poster.avif?t=1655559416\" width=560 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/c9605dd8b61f5542e6c3782e269e69dc.webm?t=1655559416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/c9605dd8b61f5542e6c3782e269e69dc.mp4?t=1655559416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use special powerups to solve seemingly unsolvable situations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/ffc92670b7abfc55a36dfbef2a31bbea.poster.avif?t=1655559416\" width=560 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/ffc92670b7abfc55a36dfbef2a31bbea.webm?t=1655559416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055270/extras/ffc92670b7abfc55a36dfbef2a31bbea.mp4?t=1655559416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
